#. <section class="sutta" id="an7.47"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "an7.47:0.1"
msgid "Aṅguttara Nikāya 7"
msgstr "Numbered Discourses 7"

#. </p><p>
msgctxt "an7.47:0.2"
msgid "5. Mahāyaññavagga"
msgstr "5. A Great Sacrifice"

#. </p><h1>
#. VAR: 47. Dutiyaaggisutta → mahāyaññasuttaṃ (bj)
msgctxt "an7.47:0.3"
msgid "47. Dutiyaaggisutta"
msgstr "47. Fires (2nd)"

#. </h1></div><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc1"></a>
#. VAR: Tena → ekaṃ samayaṃ bhagavā sāvatthiyaṃ viharati jetavane anāthapiṇḍikassa ārāme. tena (bj, s1-3)
msgctxt "an7.47:1.1"
msgid ""
"Tena kho pana samayena uggatasarīrassa brāhmaṇassa mahāyañño upakkhaṭo hoti."
msgstr ""
"Now at that time the brahmin Uggatasarīra had prepared a large sacrifice."

msgctxt "an7.47:1.2"
msgid ""
"Pañca usabhasatāni thūṇūpanītāni honti yaññatthāya, pañca vacchatarasatāni "
"thūṇūpanītāni honti yaññatthāya, pañca vacchatarisatāni thūṇūpanītāni honti "
"yaññatthāya, pañca ajasatāni thūṇūpanītāni honti yaññatthāya, pañca "
"urabbhasatāni thūṇūpanītāni honti yaññatthāya."
msgstr ""
"Bulls, bullocks, heifers, goats and rams—five hundred of each—had been led "
"to the post for the sacrifice."

msgctxt "an7.47:1.3"
msgid ""
"Atha kho uggatasarīro brāhmaṇo yena bhagavā tenupasaṅkami; upasaṅkamitvā "
"bhagavatā saddhiṃ sammodi."
msgstr ""
"Then the brahmin Uggatasarīra went up to the Buddha, and exchanged greetings "
"with him."

msgctxt "an7.47:1.4"
msgid ""
"Sammodanīyaṃ kathaṃ sāraṇīyaṃ vītisāretvā ekamantaṃ nisīdi. Ekamantaṃ "
"nisinno kho uggatasarīro brāhmaṇo bhagavantaṃ etadavoca:"
msgstr ""
"When the greetings and polite conversation were over, he sat down to one "
"side and said to the Buddha:"

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="pts-vp-pli" id="pts-vp-pli4.42"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc2"></a>
#. VAR: ādānaṃ → ādhānaṃ (s1-3, pts1)
msgctxt "an7.47:2.1"
msgid ""
"“Sutaṃ metaṃ, bho gotama, aggissa ādānaṃ yūpassa ussāpanaṃ mahapphalaṃ hoti "
"mahānisaṃsan”ti."
msgstr ""
"“Master Gotama, I have heard that kindling the sacrificial fire and raising "
"the sacrificial post is very fruitful and beneficial.”"

msgctxt "an7.47:2.2"
msgid ""
"“Mayāpi kho etaṃ, brāhmaṇa, sutaṃ aggissa ādānaṃ yūpassa ussāpanaṃ "
"mahapphalaṃ hoti mahānisaṃsan”ti."
msgstr "“I’ve also heard this, brahmin.”"

msgctxt "an7.47:2.3"
msgid "Dutiyampi kho uggatasarīro brāhmaṇo … pe …"
msgstr "For a second time …"

msgctxt "an7.47:2.4"
msgid "tatiyampi kho uggatasarīro brāhmaṇo bhagavantaṃ etadavoca:"
msgstr "and third time Uggatasarīra said to the Buddha:"

msgctxt "an7.47:2.5"
msgid ""
"“sutaṃ metaṃ, bho gotama, aggissa ādānaṃ yūpassa ussāpanaṃ mahapphalaṃ hoti "
"mahānisaṃsan”ti."
msgstr ""
"“Master Gotama, I have heard that kindling the sacrificial fire and raising "
"the sacrificial post is very fruitful and beneficial.”"

msgctxt "an7.47:2.6"
msgid ""
"“Mayāpi kho etaṃ, brāhmaṇa, sutaṃ aggissa ādānaṃ yūpassa ussāpanaṃ "
"mahapphalaṃ hoti mahānisaṃsan”ti."
msgstr "“I’ve also heard this, brahmin.”"

msgctxt "an7.47:2.7"
msgid ""
"“Tayidaṃ, bho gotama, sameti bhoto ceva gotamassa amhākañca, yadidaṃ sabbena "
"sabbaṃ”."
msgstr "“Then Master Gotama and I are in total agreement in this matter.”"

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc3"></a>
msgctxt "an7.47:3.1"
msgid "Evaṃ vutte āyasmā ānando uggatasarīraṃ brāhmaṇaṃ etadavoca:"
msgstr "When he said this, Venerable Ānanda said to Uggatasarīra:"

msgctxt "an7.47:3.2"
msgid "“na kho, brāhmaṇa, tathāgatā evaṃ pucchitabbā:"
msgstr "“Brahmin, you shouldn’t ask the Buddha in this way."

msgctxt "an7.47:3.3"
msgid ""
"‘sutaṃ metaṃ, bho gotama, aggissa ādānaṃ yūpassa ussāpanaṃ mahapphalaṃ hoti "
"mahānisaṃsan’ti."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "an7.47:3.4"
msgid "Evaṃ kho, brāhmaṇa, tathāgatā pucchitabbā:"
msgstr "You should ask in this way:"

#. VAR: aggiṃ → aggissa (mr)
#. VAR: ādātukāmo → ādhātukāmo (s1-3, pts1)
msgctxt "an7.47:3.5"
msgid "‘ahañhi, bhante, aggiṃ ādātukāmo, yūpaṃ ussāpetukāmo."
msgstr ""
"‘Sir, I want to kindle the sacrificial fire and raise the sacrificial post."

msgctxt "an7.47:3.6"
msgid "Ovadatu maṃ, bhante, bhagavā."
msgstr "May the Buddha please advise"

msgctxt "an7.47:3.7"
msgid ""
"Anusāsatu maṃ, bhante, bhagavā yaṃ mama assa dīgharattaṃ hitāya sukhāyā’”ti."
msgstr "and instruct me. It will be for my lasting welfare and happiness.’”"

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc4"></a>
msgctxt "an7.47:4.1"
msgid "Atha kho uggatasarīro brāhmaṇo bhagavantaṃ etadavoca:"
msgstr "Then Uggatasarīra said to the Buddha:"

msgctxt "an7.47:4.2"
msgid "“ahañhi, bho gotama, aggiṃ ādātukāmo yūpaṃ ussāpetukāmo."
msgstr ""
"“Sir, I want to kindle the sacrificial fire and raise the sacrificial post."

msgctxt "an7.47:4.3"
msgid "Ovadatu maṃ bhavaṃ gotamo."
msgstr "May Master Gotama please advise"

msgctxt "an7.47:4.4"
msgid ""
"Anusāsatu maṃ bhavaṃ gotamo yaṃ mama assa dīgharattaṃ hitāya sukhāyā”ti."
msgstr "and instruct me. It will be for my lasting welfare and happiness.”"

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="pts-vp-pli" id="pts-vp-pli4.43"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc5"></a>
#. VAR: ādento → ādhento (s1-3, pts1)
#. VAR: dukkhudrayāni → dukkhuddayāni (si)
msgctxt "an7.47:5.1"
msgid ""
"“Aggiṃ, brāhmaṇa, ādento yūpaṃ ussāpento pubbeva yaññā tīṇi satthāni "
"ussāpeti akusalāni dukkhudrayāni dukkhavipākāni."
msgstr ""
"“Even before kindling the sacrificial fire and raising the sacrificial post, "
"one raises three unskillful knives which ripen and result in suffering."

msgctxt "an7.47:5.2"
msgid "Katamāni tīṇi?"
msgstr "What three?"

msgctxt "an7.47:5.3"
msgid "Kāyasatthaṃ, vacīsatthaṃ, manosatthaṃ."
msgstr "The knives of the body, speech, and mind."

msgctxt "an7.47:5.4"
msgid ""
"Aggiṃ, brāhmaṇa, ādento yūpaṃ ussāpento pubbeva yaññā evaṃ cittaṃ uppādesi:"
msgstr ""
"Even before kindling the sacrificial fire and raising the sacrificial post "
"one gives rise to the thought:"

msgctxt "an7.47:5.5"
msgid ""
"‘ettakā usabhā haññantu yaññatthāya, ettakā vacchatarā haññantu yaññatthāya, "
"ettakā vacchatariyo haññantu yaññatthāya, ettakā ajā haññantu yaññatthāya, "
"ettakā urabbhā haññantu yaññatthāyā’ti."
msgstr ""
"‘May this many bulls, bullocks, heifers, goats, and rams be slaughtered for "
"the sacrifice!’"

msgctxt "an7.47:5.6"
msgid ""
"So ‘puññaṃ karomī’ti apuññaṃ karoti, ‘kusalaṃ karomī’ti akusalaṃ karoti, ‘"
"sugatiyā maggaṃ pariyesāmī’ti duggatiyā maggaṃ pariyesati."
msgstr ""
"Thinking, ‘May I make merit’, one makes bad karma. Thinking, ‘May I do good’"
", one does bad. Thinking, ‘May I seek the path to a good rebirth’, one seeks "
"the path to a bad rebirth."

msgctxt "an7.47:5.7"
msgid ""
"Aggiṃ, brāhmaṇa, ādento yūpaṃ ussāpento pubbeva yaññā idaṃ paṭhamaṃ "
"manosatthaṃ ussāpeti akusalaṃ dukkhudrayaṃ dukkhavipākaṃ."
msgstr ""
"Even before kindling the sacrificial fire and raising the sacrificial post "
"one raises this first unskillful mental knife which ripens and results in "
"suffering."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc6"></a>
msgctxt "an7.47:6.1"
msgid ""
"Puna caparaṃ, brāhmaṇa, aggiṃ ādento yūpaṃ ussāpento pubbeva yaññā evaṃ "
"vācaṃ bhāsati:"
msgstr ""
"Furthermore, even before kindling the sacrificial fire and raising the "
"sacrificial post, one says such things as:"

msgctxt "an7.47:6.2"
msgid ""
"‘ettakā usabhā haññantu yaññatthāya, ettakā vacchatarā haññantu yaññatthāya, "
"ettakā vacchatariyo haññantu yaññatthāya, ettakā ajā haññantu yaññatthāya, "
"ettakā urabbhā haññantu yaññatthāyā’ti."
msgstr ""
"‘May this many bulls, bullocks, heifers, goats, and rams be slaughtered for "
"the sacrifice!’"

msgctxt "an7.47:6.3"
msgid ""
"So ‘puññaṃ karomī’ti apuññaṃ karoti, ‘kusalaṃ karomī’ti akusalaṃ karoti, ‘"
"sugatiyā maggaṃ pariyesāmī’ti duggatiyā maggaṃ pariyesati."
msgstr ""
"Thinking, ‘May I make merit’, one makes bad karma. Thinking, ‘May I do good’"
", one does bad. Thinking, ‘May I seek the path to a good rebirth’, one seeks "
"the path to a bad rebirth."

msgctxt "an7.47:6.4"
msgid ""
"Aggiṃ, brāhmaṇa, ādento yūpaṃ ussāpento pubbeva yaññā idaṃ dutiyaṃ "
"vacīsatthaṃ ussāpeti akusalaṃ dukkhudrayaṃ dukkhavipākaṃ."
msgstr ""
"Even before kindling the sacrificial fire and raising the sacrificial post "
"one raises this second unskillful verbal knife which ripens and results in "
"suffering."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc7"></a>
#. VAR: samārambhati → samārabbhati (si, pts1, mr) | samārabhati (s1-3)
#. VAR: hantuṃ → haññantu (si, s1-3, pts1)
#. VAR: yaññatthāya → yaññatthāyāti (bj, s1-3)
msgctxt "an7.47:7.1"
msgid ""
"Puna caparaṃ, brāhmaṇa, aggiṃ ādento yūpaṃ ussāpento pubbeva yaññā sayaṃ "
"paṭhamaṃ samārambhati usabhā hantuṃ yaññatthāya, sayaṃ paṭhamaṃ samārambhati "
"vacchatarā hantuṃ yaññatthāya, sayaṃ paṭhamaṃ samārambhati vacchatariyo "
"hantuṃ yaññatthāya, sayaṃ paṭhamaṃ samārambhati ajā hantuṃ yaññatthāya, "
"sayaṃ paṭhamaṃ samārambhati urabbhā hantuṃ yaññatthāya."
msgstr ""
"Furthermore, even before kindling the sacrificial fire and raising the "
"sacrificial post one first personally undertakes preparations for the "
"sacrificial slaughter of bulls, bullocks, heifers, goats, and rams."

msgctxt "an7.47:7.2"
msgid ""
"So ‘puññaṃ karomī’ti apuññaṃ karoti, ‘kusalaṃ karomī’ti akusalaṃ karoti, ‘"
"sugatiyā maggaṃ pariyesāmī’ti duggatiyā maggaṃ pariyesati."
msgstr ""
"Thinking, ‘May I make merit’, one makes bad karma. Thinking, ‘May I do good’"
", one does bad. Thinking, ‘May I seek the path to a good rebirth’, one seeks "
"the path to a bad rebirth."

msgctxt "an7.47:7.3"
msgid ""
"Aggiṃ, brāhmaṇa, ādento yūpaṃ ussāpento pubbeva yaññā idaṃ tatiyaṃ "
"kāyasatthaṃ ussāpeti akusalaṃ dukkhudrayaṃ dukkhavipākaṃ."
msgstr ""
"Even before kindling the sacrificial fire and raising the sacrificial post, "
"one raises this third unskillful bodily knife which ripens and results in "
"suffering."

msgctxt "an7.47:7.4"
msgid ""
"Aggiṃ, brāhmaṇa, ādento yūpaṃ ussāpento pubbeva yaññā imāni tīṇi satthāni "
"ussāpeti akusalāni dukkhudrayāni dukkhavipākāni."
msgstr ""
"Even before kindling the sacrificial fire and raising the sacrificial post, "
"one raises these three unskillful knives which ripen and result in suffering."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="pts-vp-pli" id="pts-vp-pli4.44"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc8"></a>
msgctxt "an7.47:8.1"
msgid "Tayome, brāhmaṇa, aggī pahātabbā parivajjetabbā, na sevitabbā."
msgstr ""
"Brahmin, these three fires should be given up and rejected, not cultivated."

msgctxt "an7.47:8.2"
msgid "Katame tayo?"
msgstr "What three?"

msgctxt "an7.47:8.3"
msgid "Rāgaggi, dosaggi, mohaggi."
msgstr "The fires of greed, hate, and delusion."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc9"></a>
msgctxt "an7.47:9.1"
msgid "Kasmā cāyaṃ, brāhmaṇa, rāgaggi pahātabbo parivajjetabbo, na sevitabbo?"
msgstr ""
"And why should the fire of greed be given up and rejected, not cultivated?"

msgctxt "an7.47:9.2"
msgid ""
"Ratto kho, brāhmaṇa, rāgena abhibhūto pariyādinnacitto kāyena duccaritaṃ "
"carati, vācāya duccaritaṃ carati, manasā duccaritaṃ carati."
msgstr "A greedy person does bad things by way of body, speech, and mind."

msgctxt "an7.47:9.3"
msgid ""
"So kāyena duccaritaṃ caritvā, vācāya duccaritaṃ caritvā, manasā duccaritaṃ "
"caritvā kāyassa bhedā paraṃ maraṇā apāyaṃ duggatiṃ vinipātaṃ nirayaṃ "
"upapajjati."
msgstr ""
"When their body breaks up, after death, they’re reborn in a place of loss, a "
"bad place, the underworld, hell."

msgctxt "an7.47:9.4"
msgid "Tasmāyaṃ rāgaggi pahātabbo parivajjetabbo, na sevitabbo."
msgstr ""
"That’s why the fire of greed should be given up and rejected, not cultivated."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc10"></a>
msgctxt "an7.47:10.1"
msgid "Kasmā cāyaṃ, brāhmaṇa, dosaggi pahātabbo parivajjetabbo, na sevitabbo?"
msgstr ""
"And why should the fire of hate be given up and rejected, not cultivated?"

msgctxt "an7.47:10.2"
msgid ""
"Duṭṭho kho, brāhmaṇa, dosena abhibhūto pariyādinnacitto kāyena duccaritaṃ "
"carati, vācāya duccaritaṃ carati, manasā duccaritaṃ carati."
msgstr "A hateful person does bad things by way of body, speech, and mind."

msgctxt "an7.47:10.3"
msgid ""
"So kāyena duccaritaṃ caritvā, vācāya duccaritaṃ caritvā, manasā duccaritaṃ "
"caritvā kāyassa bhedā paraṃ maraṇā apāyaṃ duggatiṃ vinipātaṃ nirayaṃ "
"upapajjati."
msgstr ""
"When their body breaks up, after death, they’re reborn in a place of loss, a "
"bad place, the underworld, hell."

msgctxt "an7.47:10.4"
msgid "Tasmāyaṃ dosaggi pahātabbo parivajjetabbo, na sevitabbo."
msgstr ""
"That’s why the fire of hate should be given up and rejected, not cultivated."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc11"></a>
msgctxt "an7.47:11.1"
msgid "Kasmā cāyaṃ, brāhmaṇa, mohaggi pahātabbo parivajjetabbo, na sevitabbo?"
msgstr ""
"And why should the fire of delusion be given up and rejected, not cultivated?"

msgctxt "an7.47:11.2"
msgid ""
"Mūḷho kho, brāhmaṇa, mohena abhibhūto pariyādinnacitto kāyena duccaritaṃ "
"carati, vācāya duccaritaṃ carati, manasā duccaritaṃ carati."
msgstr "A deluded person does bad things by way of body, speech, and mind."

msgctxt "an7.47:11.3"
msgid ""
"So kāyena duccaritaṃ caritvā, vācāya duccaritaṃ caritvā, manasā duccaritaṃ "
"caritvā kāyassa bhedā paraṃ maraṇā apāyaṃ duggatiṃ vinipātaṃ nirayaṃ "
"upapajjati."
msgstr ""
"When their body breaks up, after death, they’re reborn in a place of loss, a "
"bad place, the underworld, hell."

msgctxt "an7.47:11.4"
msgid "Tasmāyaṃ mohaggi pahātabbo parivajjetabbo, na sevitabbo."
msgstr ""
"That’s why the fire of delusion should be given up and rejected, not "
"cultivated."

msgctxt "an7.47:11.5"
msgid "Ime kho tayo, brāhmaṇa, aggī pahātabbā parivajjetabbā, na sevitabbā."
msgstr "These three fires should be given up and rejected, not cultivated."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="pts-vp-pli" id="pts-vp-pli4.45"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc12"></a>
msgctxt "an7.47:12.1"
msgid ""
"Tayo kho, brāhmaṇa, aggī sakkatvā garuṃ katvā mānetvā pūjetvā sammā sukhaṃ "
"parihātabbā."
msgstr ""
"Brahmin, you should properly and happily take care of three fires, honoring, "
"respecting, esteeming, and venerating them."

msgctxt "an7.47:12.2"
msgid "Katame tayo?"
msgstr "What three?"

msgctxt "an7.47:12.3"
msgid "Āhuneyyaggi, gahapataggi, dakkhiṇeyyaggi."
msgstr ""
"The fire of those worthy of offerings dedicated to the gods. The fire of a "
"householder. And the fire of those worthy of a teacher’s offering."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc13"></a>
msgctxt "an7.47:13.1"
msgid "Katamo ca, brāhmaṇa, āhuneyyaggi?"
msgstr ""
"And what is the fire of those worthy of offerings dedicated to the gods?"

msgctxt "an7.47:13.2"
msgid ""
"Idha, brāhmaṇa, yassa te honti mātāti vā pitāti vā, ayaṃ vuccati, brāhmaṇa, "
"āhuneyyaggi."
msgstr ""
"Your mother and father are called the fire of those worthy of offerings "
"dedicated to the gods."

msgctxt "an7.47:13.3"
msgid "Taṃ kissa hetu?"
msgstr "Why is that?"

# See BB’s note for ahuta. The pun here is a direct reference to the sex magic of the Brihadarannyaka, where the “sacrificial offering” of the father is the semen, which is offered in the “sacrificial fire” of the mother’s yoni. Incubated does not really capture this!
#. VAR: Atohayaṃ → atoyaṃ (si, pts1) | atohāyaṃ (s1-3) | itopāyaṃ (mr)
msgctxt "an7.47:13.4"
msgid ""
"Atohayaṃ, brāhmaṇa, āhuto sambhūto, tasmāyaṃ āhuneyyaggi sakkatvā garuṃ "
"katvā mānetvā pūjetvā sammā sukhaṃ parihātabbo."
msgstr ""
"Since it is from them that you’ve been incubated and produced. So you should "
"properly and happily take care of this fire, honoring, respecting, "
"esteeming, and venerating it."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc14"></a>
msgctxt "an7.47:14.1"
msgid "Katamo ca, brāhmaṇa, gahapataggi?"
msgstr "And what is the fire of a householder?"

msgctxt "an7.47:14.2"
msgid ""
"Idha, brāhmaṇa, yassa te honti puttāti vā dārāti vā dāsāti vā pessāti vā "
"kammakarāti vā, ayaṃ vuccati, brāhmaṇa, gahapataggi."
msgstr ""
"Your children, partners, bondservants, workers, and staff are called a "
"householder’s fire."

msgctxt "an7.47:14.3"
msgid ""
"Tasmāyaṃ gahapataggi sakkatvā garuṃ katvā mānetvā pūjetvā sammā sukhaṃ "
"parihātabbo."
msgstr ""
"So you should properly and happily take care of this fire, honoring, "
"respecting, esteeming, and venerating it."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc15"></a>
msgctxt "an7.47:15.1"
msgid "Katamo ca, brāhmaṇa, dakkhiṇeyyaggi?"
msgstr "And what is the fire of those worthy of a teacher’s offering?"

# Here I follow BB in accepting the PTS reading madappamādā.
msgctxt "an7.47:15.2"
msgid ""
"Idha, brāhmaṇa, ye te samaṇabrāhmaṇā parappavādā paṭiviratā khantisoracce "
"niviṭṭhā ekamattānaṃ damenti, ekamattānaṃ samenti, ekamattānaṃ "
"parinibbāpenti, ayaṃ vuccati, brāhmaṇa, dakkhiṇeyyaggi."
msgstr ""
"The ascetics and brahmins who avoid intoxication and negligence, are settled "
"in patience and gentleness, and who tame, calm, and extinguish themselves "
"are called the fire of those worthy of a teacher’s offering."

msgctxt "an7.47:15.3"
msgid ""
"Tasmāyaṃ dakkhiṇeyyaggi sakkatvā garuṃ katvā mānetvā pūjetvā sammā sukhaṃ "
"parihātabbo."
msgstr ""
"So you should properly and happily take care of this fire, honoring, "
"respecting, esteeming, and venerating it."

msgctxt "an7.47:15.4"
msgid ""
"Ime kho, brāhmaṇa, tayo aggī sakkatvā garuṃ katvā mānetvā pūjetvā sammā "
"sukhaṃ parihātabbā."
msgstr ""
"You should properly and happily take care of these three fires, honoring, "
"respecting, esteeming, and venerating them."

# This last is a curious piece of advice. perhaps the Buddha is hinting that the whole fire thing is best “put aside”.
#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc16"></a>
msgctxt "an7.47:16.1"
msgid ""
"Ayaṃ kho pana, brāhmaṇa, kaṭṭhaggi kālena kālaṃ ujjaletabbo, kālena kālaṃ "
"ajjhupekkhitabbo, kālena kālaṃ nibbāpetabbo, kālena kālaṃ nikkhipitabbo”ti."
msgstr ""
"But the wood fire, brahmin, should, from time to time, be fanned, watched "
"over with equanimity, extinguished, or put aside.”"

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="pts-vp-pli" id="pts-vp-pli4.46"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc17"></a>
msgctxt "an7.47:17.1"
msgid "Evaṃ vutte, uggatasarīro brāhmaṇo bhagavantaṃ etadavoca:"
msgstr "When he said this, the brahmin Uggatasarīra said to the Buddha:"

msgctxt "an7.47:17.2"
msgid "“abhikkantaṃ, bho gotama, abhikkantaṃ, bho gotama … pe …"
msgstr "“Excellent, Master Gotama! Excellent! …"

msgctxt "an7.47:17.3"
msgid "upāsakaṃ maṃ bhavaṃ gotamo dhāretu ajjatagge pāṇupetaṃ saraṇaṃ gatanti."
msgstr ""
"From this day forth, may Master Gotama remember me as a lay follower who has "
"gone for refuge for life."

msgctxt "an7.47:17.4"
msgid ""
"Esāhaṃ, bho gotama, pañca usabhasatāni muñcāmi jīvitaṃ demi, pañca "
"vacchatarasatāni muñcāmi jīvitaṃ demi, pañca vacchatarisatāni muñcāmi "
"jīvitaṃ demi, pañca ajasatāni muñcāmi jīvitaṃ demi, pañca urabbhasatāni "
"muñcāmi jīvitaṃ demi."
msgstr ""
"Master Gotama, I now set free these five hundred bulls, five hundred "
"bullocks, five hundred heifers, five hundred goats, and five hundred rams. I "
"give them life!"

#. VAR: vāto → vāyo (bj)
#. VAR: upavāyatan”ti → vāyatūti (bj) | upavāyatūti (s1-3, pts1, mr)
msgctxt "an7.47:17.5"
msgid ""
"Haritāni ceva tiṇāni khādantu, sītāni ca pānīyāni pivantu, sīto ca nesaṃ "
"vāto upavāyatan”ti."
msgstr "May they eat grass and drink cool water and enjoy a cool breeze!”"

#. </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "an7.47:17.6"
msgid "Catutthaṃ."
msgstr ""
